dc_title_s: Land Use (Future) St. Croix County, WI 2013
dc_description_s: This polygon data layer represents future land use for St. Croix County, Wisconsin in 2013. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, St_Croix_LandUse_2013.gdb. [General Land Use] [1993 Land Use Survey done by West Central Wisconsin Regional Planning Commission]
uw_supplemental_s: This metadata was updated to reflect that the data is no longer restricted and has been opened for public use. For current data access please visit http://sccgis-scccdd.opendata.arcgis.com/
